Functional disability associated with disease and quality-of-life parameters in 
Chinese patients with rheumatoid arthritis.

Ji J(1), Zhang L(1)(2), Zhang Q(1)(2), Yin R(1)(2), Fu T(1)(2), Li L(3), Gu 
Z(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Rheumatology, Affiliated Hospital of Nantong University, 20th 
